{'DISEASE: Note=A chromosomal aberration involving NCOA1 is a cause of rhabdomyosarcoma. Translocation t(2', 'Delayed sleep phase syndrome (DSPS) [MIM', '2)(q35', 'p23) with PAX3 generates the NCOA1-PAX3 oncogene consisting of the N-terminus part of PAX3 and the C-terminus part of NCOA1.
